docs.abstract: The Federal Reserve cut its benchmark interest rate a quarter point as it tried to insulate the economy from President Trump’s trade war and a global slowdown.

docs.lead_paragraph: SEOUL, South Korea — As tensions between Tokyo and Seoul have surged in recent months, South Koreans have shown their anger with their wallets. Japanese beer is going unsold.
